ies)\n- 3 Levels from Medium to Planet size!\n(maps take place on different planets)\n- Latest Gen Graphics and FX \n- Special PickUps to choose\n- Unlimited Survival mode play as long as you can survive!\n- Outstanding Sound FX and Music Tracks!\n- Leaderboards to track your ranking among other players worldwide\n\nTake them down Hunter!", "short_description": "Hunt down Monsters in a Sci-Fi Horror Survival Shooter and test your Skills among other other player!\nLive a immersive experience with latest generation graphics for Go and GearVR!"}]}, "developer_name": "Anomos Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": null, "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.anomos-studios.com/about", "publisher_name": "Anomos Studios", "support_website_url": "https://www.anomos-studios.com/", "website_url": "https://www.anomos-studios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "SHOOTER", "HORROR"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "620472595732415"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 42, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "203056001227763"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "377374499943589"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "796582560876291"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "300526474950496"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "325727185438482"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2633516883591381"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "333229967716532"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "680359379635988"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1237774223341843"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "124992672073122